owl:Ontology.dc:description: The Friend of a Friend (FOAF) RDF vocabulary, described using W3C RDF Schema and the Web Ontology Language.
owl:Ontology.dc:title: Friend of a Friend (FOAF) vocabulary

owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:comment: Indicates the class of individuals that are a member of a Group
owl:AnnotationProperty.rdfs:label: membershipClass

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A thing depicted in this representation.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: depicts

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: A person known by this person (indicating some level of reciprocated interaction between the parties).
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: knows

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: Something that was made by this agent.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: made

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: An agent that made this thing.
owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:label: maker

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The age in years of some agent.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: age

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The birthday of this Agent, represented in mm-dd string form, eg. '12-31'.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: birthday

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The family name of some person.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: familyName

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The first name of a person.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: firstName

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The gender of this Agent (typically but not necessarily 'male' or 'female').
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: gender

owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:comment: The last name of a person.
owl:DatatypeProperty.rdfs:label: lastName

owl:Class.rdfs:comment: An agent (eg. person, group, software or physical artifact).
owl:Class.rdfs:label: Agent
